        <mxCell id="mmrgZ31232cfRxLB8HJS-30" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Ultiliza a matriz já superamostrada com os dados de cada target e o vetor de pulsos para gerar a saida s(t).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;a saida s(t) tem os dados já contidos dentro da fase, amplitude e frequência do sinal.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;A sintese aqui é:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- converter distância em intensidade (utilizando ganho, distância, rcs, etc).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;- calcular desvio doppler com a velocidade do alvo.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="760" y="410" width="120" height="380" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="mmrgZ31232cfRxLB8HJS-31" value="" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;rounded=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.25;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;exitX=0.5;exitY=0;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="mmrgZ31232cfRxLB8HJS-22" target="mmrgZ31232cfRxLB8HJS-27">
          <mxGeometry width="50" height="50" relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="600" y="310" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="765" y="375" as="targetPoint" />
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="420" y="200" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="mmrgZ31232cfRxLB8HJS-32" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Com base nas especificações passadas na simulação, gera um vetor de pulsos de radar de t0 a t1 e fs, esses pulsos ja contem dentro de si informação de desvio de fase/freq (doppler), amplitude (rsc / ganho / distância), etc.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;também exporta os pulsos sem alteração para comparação e processamento.&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="760" y="-100" width="120" height="270" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
